   the byte/offset it reads.  same[hpos]==3 nails the run-length loop.  val2==7
   == ((3-ZOPFLI_MIN_MATCH)&255)^7 nails the second hash.  prev/prev2==5 and
   head/head2==hpos nail both chain updates. */
